hadiths[238]{hadithnumber,text}:
2882,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safar azab ka eik tukda hai. wo aadmi ko neend sey aur khaney peeney sey rok deta hai, isliye jab koi apney safar sey maqsud kaam pura kar ley to usey chahiye ke jaldi ghar lot aaye. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Yaqub bin Humed bin Kaasib key wastey sey ye riwayat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah bayan ki hai."
2883,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas ya Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Haj ka irada rakhta ho to usey chahiye ke jaldi karey kyonkey mumkin hai aadmi bimar ho jaey, ya uski sawari gum ho jaey ya koi aur zarurat pesh aa jaey (jis ki wajeh sey wo Haj na kar sakey)."
2884,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab ye aayat nazil hui : ( وَلِلَّـهِ عَلَى النَّاسِ حِجُّ الْبَيْتِ مَنِ اسْتَطَاعَ إِلَيْهِ سَبِيلًا ),''Allah taala ney un logon par jo uski taraf raah paa saktey hon, us ghar ka Haj farz kar diya hai.'' to Sahaba ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya har saal Haj karna farz hai?  Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey. unhoney phir kaha : kya har saal? aap ney farmaya : nahin. aur agar main haan keh deta to (har saal ada karna) farz ho jata. tab ye aayat nazil hui : (يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا لَا تَسْأَلُوا عَنْ أَشْيَاءَ إِن تُبْدَ لَكُمْ تَسُؤْكُمْ),''aey eman walo ! aisi baaten mat poochho ke agar wo tum par zahir kar di jaeyn to tumhen nagawar hon.''"
2885,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya Haj har saal karna farz hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main haan keh deta to wo farz ho jata, aur agar wo farz ho jata to tum isey (pabandi sey) ada na kar saktey, aur agar tum isey pabandi sey ada na kartey to tumhen azab hota."
2886,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aqra bin Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya Haj har saal (ada karna farz) hai ya (zindagi mein) eik hi baar? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : balke eik hi baar (farz hai).  phir jisey taqat ho to wo nafli Haj ada kar ley.
2887,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj aur Umerey musalsal kartey raha karo kyonkey unhein pay dar pai ada karna muflisi aur gunahon ko is tarah door kar deta hai jis tarah bhatti lohey key mail kuchail ko door kar deti hai.  Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Muhammad bin Bishr key wastey sey ye riwayat bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sabiqa hadees key hum maana bayan ki hai."
2888,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik Umerey key baad doosra Umra dono ki darmiyani muddat key gunahon ka kaffara ho jata hai. aur Haj mabroor (nekiyon waley Haj) ka badla mehaz jannat hai."
2889,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs is ghar (Kaaba Shareef) ka Haj karey aur) Haj key doran mein) be-hooda goi na karey aur gunah na karey, wo wapis aata hai to is tarah (gunahon sey paak) hota hai jaisey wo apni maa sey paida hotey waqt tha."
2890,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik puraney kajawey par aur eik aisi (maamuli) chadar odh kar Haj ada kiya jiski qeemat chaar dirham thi, chaar dirham key barabar bhi na thi. aur farmaya : aey Allah ! Haj (key farz ki adaaegi maqsood) hai, dikhlaao aur shohrat (maqsood) nahin."
2891,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Makkey aur Madiney key darmiyan Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. hum eik wadi sey guzrey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye kon si wadi hai? Sahaba ney arz kiya : ye wadiye Azraq hai. aap ney farmaya : goya main Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekh raha hun. aap ney unkey baalon ki lambaai key barey mein kuchh farmaya (jo Raavi hadees) Dawud (bin Abi Hind) ko yad nahin raha.  unhoney kanon mein ungliyan dali hui hain, wo Allah sey buland aawaz sey fariyad kartey huye labbaik pukartey huye us wadi sey guzar rahey hain. Sahaba ney farmaya : phir hamney safar jari rakha yahan tak key eik ghaati tak pahunchey to aap ney farmaya : ye kon si ghaati hai? logon ney kaha : Harsha ya laft ki ghaati hai. aap ney farmaya : main goya Yunus (Alaihissalam) ko dekh raha hun jo surkh oontni par sawar hain. oon ka jubba odhey huye hain. un ki oontni ki mahaar (nakel) khajoor ki rassi ki hai aur wo labbaik pukartey huye us wadi sey guzar rahey hain."
2892,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj aur Umra karney waley Allah Taala key mulaaqaati (aur mehman) hain. agar wo Allah sey dua karen to Allah un ki dua qubul karta hai aur agar wo bakhshish maangen to unhein bakhsh deta hai."
2893,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki raah mein jang karney wala (Mujahid), Haaji aur umra karney wala Allah key mehman hain. usney unhein bulaya to unhoney taameel ki. unhoney Allah sey manga to Allah ney dey diya."
2894,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey umra karney ki ijazat chahi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ijazat dey di, aur farmaya : bhai ! apni kisi dua mein hamein bhi shareek kar lena aur (dua mein) hamein na bhoolna."
2895,"Hazrat Safwan bin Abdullah bin Safwan (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti un (Safwan) key nikah mein thin. wo unkey yahan aaye to Umme Dardaa (Raziallahu anha) sey mulaqat hui, Hazrat Abu Dardaa (Raziallahu anhu) (ghar mein) na miley. Umme Dardaa (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : aap ka is saal Haj ka irada hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan. farmaya : to hamarey liye bhi duaaey khair karna kyonkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aadmi ki apney bhai key haq mein uski adam mojudgi mein ki hui dua maqbool hai. dua karney waley key sar key qarib eik farishta uski dua par Aameen kehta hai. jab bhi wo us (ghair mojud bhai) key haq mein dua karta hai. farishta kehta hai : Aameen aur tujhey bhi yehi kuchh nasib ho. unhoney farmaya : phir main bazar gaya to Hazrat Abu Dardaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey mulaqat ho gaee to unhoney bhi mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka yehi farman sunaya."
2896,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik shakhs uth kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qarib gaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis chiz sey Haj wajib hota hai? aap ney farmaya : safar kharch aur sawari sey. usney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool : Haaji kon hota hai? aap ney farmaya : bikhre baalon wala, saada libas wala. eik aur shakhs ney uth kar kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Haj kya hota hai? farmaya : aawaz buland karna aur khoon bahana. Imam Wakee ney farmaya : aawaz sey murad buland aawaz sey labbaik pukarna hai aur khoon bahaney sey murad oont qurban karna hai."
2897,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Allah Taala key farman : (مَنِ اسْتَطَاعَ إِلَيْهِ سَبِيلًا), ''jis ko Baitullah tak raasta tey karney ki taqat ho.'' ki wazahat mein farmaya : (us taqat sey murad hai) safar kharch aur sawari."
2898,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aurat teen din ya ziyada ka safar na karey magar apney baap , bhai , betey , khawind ya kisi aur mehram key sath."
2899,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aurat Allah aur qiyamat par eman rakhti hai uskey liye eik din ka safar karna halal nahin jabke uskey sath Mohrim na ho."
2900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : mera naam falan falan ghazwey mein likha gaya hai aur meri aurat Haj key liye rawana ho chuki hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uskey saath chala ja."
2901,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aurton par bhi jihad farz hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan ! un par aisa jihad farz hai jis mein jang nahin hoti. wo Haj aur umra hai."
2902,"Ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Haj har kamzor ka jihad hai."
2903,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ko yun kehtey suna : Shabarma ki taraf sey labbaik. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Shabarma kon hai? usney kaha : mera qaribi rishtedar hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum ney (pehley) kabhi Haj kiya hai? usney kaha nahin. aap ney farmaya : ye Haj apni taraf sey kar, phir (baad mein) Shabarma ki taraf sey karna."
2904,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : kya main apney walid ki taraf sey Haj kar sakta hun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, apney walid ki taraf sey Haj kar. agar to uskey liye bhalai mein izafa nahin kerega to burai mein bhi izafa nahin karega."
2905,"Hazrat Abu-ghaus bin Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) jo maqame-Faraa' key rehney waley they, un sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey fatwa puchha ke unkey walid key zimmey Haj tha aur wo Haj kiye baghair faut ho gaey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney walid ki taraf sey Haj karo. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar key rozon ka bhi yehi hukm hai ke uski taraf sey ada kiye jaeyn."
2906,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen Uqeli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid bahut boodhey hain, na Haj aur umra ada kar saktey hain aur na sawari par sawar ho saktey hain. aap ney farmaya : apney walid ki taraf sey Haj aur umra karo."
2907,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke qabila Khasam ki eik khatoon Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid sahab boodhey hain. wo intehai boodhey ho chukey hain aur Haj ka jo farz Allah ki taraf sey bandon par aaid hota hai, wo un par bhi lazim ho gaya hai aur wo (khud) isey ada karney ki taqat nahin rakhtey. agar main un ki taraf sey ye farz ada kar dun to kya un ki taraf sey kafi hoga? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan."
2908,"Hazrat Husain bin Auf (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey walid par Haj farz ho gaya hai. wo Haj nahin kar saktey siwaye iskey ke unhein sawari par baandh diya jaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kuchh der khamosh rahey, phir farmaya : apney walid ki taraf sey Haj karo."
2909,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney apney bhai Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat ki ke qurbani key din wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey (oontni par) sawar they. qabila Khasam ki eik khatoon ney hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ney bandon par Haj ka jo fariza aaid kiya hai, wo merey walid par is haal mein lazim huwa hai ke wo bahut boodhey ho gaey hain, sawar nahin ho saktey. kya main un ki taraf sey Haj karun? aap ney farmaya : haan. agar tumharey walid par qarz hota to tum usey ada kartin (isi tarah Allah ka qarz bhi ada karo)."
2910,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Haj (key safar) key doran main eik aurat ney apna bachcha buland kar key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dikhaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya is ( bachchey) ka bhi Haj hai? aap ney farmaya : haan, aur tujhey sawab hai."
2911,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : maqame-shajra (zul-haleefa key maqam) par Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) key yahan wiladat ho gaee. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke unhein ghusl karney aur ehraam baandhney ka hukm den."
2912,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj key liye rawana huye to unkey sath Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) bhi thin. maqame-shajra (zul-haleefa) par unkey yahan Muhammad bin Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhuma) paida huye. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar khabar di. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke unhein (Asmaa (Raziallahu anha) ko) hukm den ke ghusl kar key Haj ka ehraam baandh lein, phir wo sab kaam karen jo Haaji karta hai magar Baitullah ka tawaf na karen."
2913,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) key yahan Muhammad bin Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anhuma) paida huye to unhoney (masla malum karney key liye) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bheja (ke ab kya karun)? aap ney unhein hukm diya ke ghusl karen aur eik kapdey ko langot ki tarah baandh lein aur labbaik pukaren (ehraam baandh lein)."
2914,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Madiney waley Zul-Hulefa sey ehraam baandhen, Sham waley Johfa sey aur Najad waley qarn-al-manaazil sey. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ye teen mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suney hain aur mujhey khabar mili hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : aur Yamen waley yalamlam sey ehraam baandhen."
2915,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya aur farmaya : Madiney walon key liye ehraam ki jagah Zul-Hulefa hai. Sham walon key liye ehraam ki jagah Johfa hai. Yamen walon key liye ehraam ki jagah yalamlam hai. Najad walon key liye ehraam ki jagah qarn hai. Mashriq (Iraaq) walon key liye ehraam ki jagah zaatil-arq hai. iskey baad aap ney (mashriq key) ufaq ki taraf chehra kar key farmaya : aey Allah ! in key dilon ko (deen ki taraf) mutawajjeh kar dey."
2916,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab rikaab mein qadam rakhtey aur aap ki sawari aap ko ley kar khadi ho jati to Zul-Hulefa ki masjid key paas sey labbaik pukartey.
2917,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main darkht key paas (zul-haleefa mein) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni key ghutnon key paas tha. jab wo aap ko ley kar puri tarah khadi ho gaee to aap ney farmaya : Haj aur umra dono key liye labbaik. aur ye Hajjatul-Wadaa ka waqiyaa hai."
2918,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey talbiya seekha. aap keh rahey they : (لَبَّيْكَ اللَّهُمَّ , لَبَّيْكَ لَبَّيْكَ , لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ لَبَّيْكَ , إِنَّ الْحَمْدَ وَالنِّعْمَةَ لَكَ وَالْمُلْكَ , لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ), ''hazir hun, aey Allah ! main hazir hun. main hazir hun, tera koi shareek nahin, main hazir hun, tareefen aur nematen teri hain aur badshahi bhi. tera koi shareek nahin.'' Imam Nafey (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) in alfaz ka izafa kartey they : (لَبَّيْكَ لَبَّيْكَ ! لَبَّيْكَ وَسَعْدَيْكَ , وَالْخَيْرُ فِي يَدَيْكَ لَبَّيْكَ , وَالرَّغْبَاءُ إِلَيْكَ وَالْعَمَلُ), ''hazir hun ! hazir hun ! teri itaat ki khush naseebi mujhe haasil hai, aur har qism ki khair terey haathon mein hai. main hazir hun ! (dil mein) teri hi lagan hai aur (terey hi liye) amal.''"
2919,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka talbiya ye tha : (لَبَّيْكَ ! اللَّهُمَّ لَبَّيْكَ ! لَبَّيْكَ ! لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ لَبَّيْكَ , إِنَّ الْحَمْدَ وَالنِّعْمَةَ لَكَ وَالْمُلْكَ , لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ), ''hazir hun ! aey Allah hazir hun, main hazir hun, tera koi shareek nahin, hazir hun ! tareefen aur nematen teri hi hain aur badshahi bhi, tera koi shareek nahin."""
2920,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney talbiye mein farmaya : ( لَبَّيْكَ إِلَهَ الْحَقِّ , لَبَّيْكَ ), ''hazir hun, aey sachchey mabood ! main hazir hun ! ."""
2921,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi talbiya kehney wala labbaik pukarta hai, uskey daain baain dono taraf zamin ki inteha tak har patthar , darkht aur eent (har chiz) labbaik pukaarti hai."
2922,Hazrat Khallad bin Saaib (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid (Hazrat Saaib bin Khallad bin Suwed (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney merey paas aa kar mujhey kaha ke main apney sathiyon ko hukm dun ke labbaik buland aawaz sey pukaren.
2923,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey paas Jibril (Alaihissalam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : aey Muhammad ((Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ! apney sathiyon ko hukm dijiye ke labbaik buland aawaz sey pukara karen kyonkey ye Haj key shiaar (khaas kaam) mein shamil hai."
2924,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kiya gaya : kon sa amal afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : aawaz buland karna (labbaik buland aawaz sey kehna) aur khoon bahana (qurbani karna)."
2925,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ehraam wala Allah ki raza key liye din bhar dhoop mein labbaik pukarta hai yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho jaey to suraj uskey gunahon samet ghurub hota hai (jis tarah suraj ghurub ho gaya, is tarah uskey gunah khatam ho gaey). aur wo is tarah (gunahon sey paak saaf) ho jata hai jaisey wo apni maa sey paida huwa tha."
2926,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key ehraam baandhney key waqt ehraam baandhney sey pehley khushbu lagai aur ehraam kholney key waqt tawafe ifaaza karney sey pehley bhi. Sufiyan ki riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : (mainey) apney in dono haathon sey (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khushbu lagai."
2927,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : goya main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) labbaik pukar rahey hain."
2928,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : goya main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mein khushbu ki chamak dekh rahi hun jabke aap ko ehraam baandhey teen din ho chukey hain."
2929,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : Mohrim kon sey kapdey pehan sakta hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qameez , pagdi, shalwaar, barns aur mozey na pehney, albatta agar kisi ko jootey dastyaab na hon to mozey pehan ley aur unhen takhnon key nichey sey kaat ley (taake jooton ki tarah bin jaeyn). aur aisa koi kapda na pahno jisey za'fraan ya waras lagi ho."
2930,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam waley ko waras ya za'fraan sey ranga huwa kapda pehanney sey mana farmaya."
2931,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par khutba detey suna , aap ney farmaya : jisey tehband na miley , wo paajaama (ya shalwaar) pehan ley. aur jisey jootay na milen , wo mozey pehan ley. Hisham ki riwayat mein ye alfaz bhi hain : kapda na honey ki surat mein paajaama bhi pehan sakta hai."
2932,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey jootey muyassar na hon , wo mozey pehan ley aur unhen takhnon sey nichey tak kaat dey (taake jootey bin jaeyn)."
2933,"Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath rawana huye yahan tak key jab hum maqam araj par pahunchey to (aaram karney key liye) thehrey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bethey huye they. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethi thin. main Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethi thi. hamara aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka (samane-safar wala) oont eik hi tha. jo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key ghulam key paas tha. wo ghulam aaya to uskey paas oont na tha. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tera oont kahan hai? usney kaha : raat ko gum ho gaya. unhoney farmaya : sirf eik oont aur wo bhi tu ney gum kar diya? aur usey maarney lagey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein insan) ko dekhen, kya kar rahey hain?"
2934,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Hunain (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke maqame-Abwaa par Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas aur Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anha) key darmiyan (eik masle mein) ikhtilaf ho gaya. Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) kehtey they ke mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein insan) sar dho sakta hai jabkey Hazrat Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein insan) sar nahin dho sakta. (Hazrat Abdullah bin Hunain ney kaha)  Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anha) ney mujhey ye masla malum karney key liye Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja. mainey unhen kunwen ki do lakdiyon key darmiyan ghusl kartey paya. unhoney eik kapdey sey parda kar rakha tha. mainey salam kiya to unhoney farmaya : kon hai? mainey kaha : main Abdullah bin Hunain hun. mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney aap ki khidmat mein ye poochhney key liye bheja hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ehraam ki haalat mein apna sar kis tarah dhotey they? Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) ney kapdey par haath rakh kar usey itna nichey kar diya ke mujhey unka sar nazar aaney laga, phir us shakhs ko jo (nahaney mein madad detey huye) aap par pani dal raha tha, farmaya : pani dalo. usney aap key sar par pani dala to aap ney dono haathon sey apney sar (key baalon) ko harkat di. aap apney haathon ko aagey ki taraf bhi laye aur peechhey bhi ley gaey. phir farmaya : mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is tarah kartey dekha hai."
2935,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they aur hamney ehraam baandha huwa tha. jab hamein koi sawar nazar aata to hum apney saron sey kapdey (chehrey par) latka letin. aur jab wo guzar jata, hum kapda utha letin. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Ali bin Muhammad ki sanad sey ye riwayat bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sabiqa hadees key hum maana bayan ki hai."
2936,Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Rahimahullah) bin Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) apni daadi Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) ya apni naani Hazrat Sa'di binte Auf (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Zabaa binte Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anha) key yahan tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : phuphi jaan ! aap ko Haj karney mein kya rukawat darpesh hai? unhoney kaha : main bimar aurat hun aur raastey mein ruk janey (aur safar jari na rakh sakney) sey darti hun. aap ney farmaya : ehraam baandh lijiye aur shart kar lijiye ke aap wahin ehraam khol dengi jahan aap ko rukawat pesh aa jaey.
2937,"Hazrat Zabaa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye jabkey main bimar thi. aap ney farmaya : kya is saal tumhara Haj ka iraada nahin hai? mainey kha : Allah key Rasool ! main bimar hun : aap ney farmaya : Haj karo aur keh do : (aey Allah) main wahan ehraam khol dungi jahan to mujhey rok dey."
2938,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Zabaa binte Zuber bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : main bhari jism ki (ya bimar) aurat hun aur main Haj ka irada rakhti hun. main kaisey ehraam baandhon? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ehraam baandh lo aur shart laga lo ke main wahin ehraam khol dungi jahan (aey Allah ! ) to mujhey rok ley."
2939,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Anbiyaae-Kiraam chaltey huey (sawari key baghair) aur nangey paon Haram mein dakhil huwa kartey they aur (isi tarah) Baitu-llah ka tawaf kartey they. wo tamam manaasik (aur kaam) pedal aur nangey paon ada kartey they."
2940,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein saniyatil-uliyaa sey dakhil hotey they. aur jab (Makka shareef sey) bahar nikaltey to saniyatil-suflaa sey nikaltey they.
2941,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein din key waqt dakhil huye.
2942,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kal aap kahan qiyam farmaeyngey? ye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key doran ka waqiyaa hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya Aqeel ney hamarey liye koi ghar chhoda hai? َphir farmaya : hum kal banu Kinaana key kheef (wadi mohsib) mein thehrengey jahan Quraish ney kufr par qaaim rehney key liye aapas mein qasmen khai thin. ye us waqiye ki taraf ishara hai jab banu Kinaana ney Quraish sey qasmen kha kar banu Haashim key khilaf muahida kiya tha ke banu Haashim sey rishta naataa nahin kerengey aur un sey kharid aur farokht bhi nahin kerengey. Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ""kheef"" wadi ko kehtey hain."
2943,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kam baalon waley umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo Hajare-Aswad ko bosa detey aur farmatey they : main tujhey choom raha hun, halanke main janta hun ke to mehaz eik patthar hai, na kisi ko nuqsan pahuncha sakta hai, na nafa dey sakta hai. agar mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tujhey choomtey na dekha hota to tujhey na choomta."
2944,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din ye patthar (Hajare-Aswad) zarur is haal mein hazir hoga ke uski do aankhen hongi jin sey wo dekhega, aur zaban hogi jis sey wo boleyga. jisney isey haq key sath choomaa hoga uskey haq mein gawahi dega."
2945,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hajare-Aswad ki taraf aaye, phir is par hont Mubarak rakh kar der tak rotey rahey, phir mud kar dekha to Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) rotey nazar aaye. tab aap ney farmaya : umr ! is maqam par aansu bahaaey jatey hain."
2946,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah key konon mein sey sirf Hajare-Aswad ka aur banu Jamah key gharon ki taraf waaqey Hajare-Aswad sey muttasil (lage huey) koney (rukne-Yamaani) ka istilaam kartey they."
2947,"Hazrat Safiya bint Sheeba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Fateh Makka key saal jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (Fateh sey mutalliq maamlat niptaa kar) itminan hasil huwa to aap ney oont par sawar ho kar tawaf kiya. (us doran mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney haath mein mojud chhadi key sath istilaam (chhuaa) kartey they, phir aap Kaba Shareef key andar dakhil huye to uskey andar khajoor ki lakdi sey bani hui eik kabootri nazar aai. aap ney isey tod diya, phir Kaba key darwazey par khadey ho kar usey (Kaabe sey bahir) phenk diya. aur main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (kabootri ka but Kaabe sey bahar phainktey) dekh rahi thi."
2948,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hajjatul-wadaa key doran mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney oont par sawar ho kar tawaf kiya aur chhadi sey Hajare-Aswad ka istilaam  kartey (chhute) rahey.
2949,"Hazrat Abu-Tufail Aamir bin Waasila (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap sawari par Baitullah ka tawaf kar rahey they. aap chhadi key sath Hajare-Aswad ka istilaam kartey aur chhadi ko bosa detey they."
2950,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab pehli baar Baitullah ka tawaf kartey to teen chakkaron mein ramal kartey (tez raftaar chalte) aur chaar chakkaron mein (aam raftaar sey) chaltey,Hajar sey Hajar tak. (Nafey ney farmaya) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) bhi isi tarah kartey they."
2951,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen chakkaron mein Hajar sey Hajar tak ramal kiya (tez raftaar chalen) aur chaar chakkaron mein (aam raftaar sey) chaley.
2952,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ab ramal ka kya faeyda hai jabke Allah Taala ney Islam ko mustehkam (mazboot) kar diya hai aur kufr aur ehale-kufr ko mulk (Arab) sey nikal diya hai? aur qism hai Allah ki ! hum wo kaam nahin chodengey jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein kiya kartey they."
2953,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke suleh-hudaibia key baad jab Umerey key moqey par Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney Makka Mukarrama mein dakhil honey ka irada kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : kal tumhari qom key log tumhen dekhengey, lihaza zaruri hai ke tum unhein mazbut nazar aao. chunanche jab Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum Masjide-Haram mein dakhil huye to unhoney Hajare-Aswad ko bosa diya aur ramal kiya (tez chaal se chale), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi unkey sath they. jab wo hazraat rukne Yamaani par pahunchey to Hajare-Aswad tak (aam chaal sey) chal kar gaey . phir ramal kiya yahan tak key rukne Yamaani tak pahunch gaey. phir Hajare-Aswad tak chal kar gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi teen baar isi tarah (ramal) kiya, phir chaar baar (daudey) baghair chal kar tawaf kiya."
2954,Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney iztibaa ki haalat mein tawaf kiya. (Raavi hadees) Qabisa ney kaha : aap ney eik chadar odhi hui thi.
2955,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Hajar (Hateem) key barey mein sawal kiya to aap ney farmaya : wo bhi Kaba mein shamil hai. mainey kaha : phir unhoney kis rukawat ki wajeh sey usey Kaba (ki imarat) mein shamil nahin kiya? aap ney farmaya : unkey paas (halal maal sey) kharch khatam ho gaya tha.  mainey kaha : uska darwaza buland kyon hai ke seedhi key baghair chadha nahin ja sakta? aap ney farmaya : ye teri qom ka kaam hai. (un ka maqsad ye tha) ke jisey chahen Kaabe mein dakhil honey den aur jisey chahen rok den. agar tari qom ka kufr ka zamana qarib na hota aur ye khof na hota ke unkey dil mutnaffar (nafrat bhare dil) ho jaeyngey to main ghaur karta ke aaya isey tabdeel kar key iska wo hissa bhi is mein shamil kar dun jo kam kar diya gaya hai, aur main iska darwaza zamin par (satah key barabar) banata."
2956,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna : jo shakhs Baitullah ka tawaf karey aur do rakat namaz padhey, (uska) ye (amal) eik insan azad karney ki tarah hai."
2957,"Hazrat Humed bin Abu-Suya (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey ibne-Hisham (Rahimahullah) ko suna ke wo Hazrat Ata bin abi Ribah (Rahimahullah) sey rukne-Yamaani key barey mein sawal kar rahey they jabke wo baitullah shareef ka tawaf kar rahey they. Hazrat Ata (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is par sattar farishtey muqarrar hain jo shakhs ye dua padhta hai farishtey (uski dua par) Aameen kehtey hain (dua ye hai) ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ الْعَفْوَ وَالْعَافِيَةَ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ رَبَّنَا آتِنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةً وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ حَسَنَةً وَقِنَا عَذَابَ النَّارِ ) aey Allah ! main tujh sey duniya aur aakhirat mein maafi aur aafiyat ka sawal karta hun . aey hamarey Malik ! hamen duniya mein bhi bhalai ata farma aur aakhirat mein bhi bhalai ata farma. aur hamen aag key azab sey bacha. jab wo Hajare-Aswad par pahunchey to kaha : abu-Muhammad ! aap ko us Hajare-Aswad key barey mein kya hadees pahunchi hai? Ata (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna . jo shakhs uski taraf mutawajjeh hota hai wo Rehman key haath ki taraf mutawajjeh hota hai. ibne-Hisham (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : abu-Muhammad! aur tawaf? Ata (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs Kaba key saat chakkar lagata hai aur) us doran mein) sirf yehi kehta hai, ( سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَلَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّہ ) Allah pak hai. tamam taarifein Allah key liye hain. Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah ki tofiq key baghair koi bachao aur taqat nahin. uskey das gunah maaf ho jatey hain, aur uskey liye das nekiyan likhi jati hain, aur uski wajeh sey uskey das darjey buland ho jatey hain. aur jo shakhs tawaf karta hai aur us haal mein baat cheet karta hai, wo rehmat mein apney qadam hi dakhil karta hai, jaisey koi pani mein paon dakhil kerey."
2958,"Hazrat Muttalib bin Abu-Wadaaa Sehami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap saat chakkaron sey farigh huye to tashrif ley aaye yahan tak key Hajare-Aswad key barabar aagey. phir aap ney Mataaf (tawaf ki jagah) key kinarey par do rakatein padhin jabke aap key aur tawaf karney walon key darmiyan koi (sutarah) na tha. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye hukm (logon key namazi key aagey sey guzartey rehney key bawajud namaz padhtey rehna) sirf Makka key sath khas hai. (masjid haram mein ye ijazat hai, aur kahin nahin.)"
2959,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Kaba key gird saat chakkar lagaey , phir do rakatein padhin.) Imam (Wakee ney farmaya : maqame-Ibrahim key paas. phir (masjid sey) nikal kar Safa ki taraf tashrif ley gaey."
2960,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Baitullah shareef key tawaf sey farigh huye to Maqame-Ibrahim par tashrif ley gaey . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! ye hamarey Buzurg Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ka maqam hai jis key barey mein Allah Subhanahu o Taala ney farmaya hai : ( وَاتَّخِذُوا مِنْ مَقَامِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ )' Ibrahim key khadey honey ki jagah ko namaz ki jagah banao . Hazrat Waleed bin Muslim (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : mainey Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) sey daryaft kya : kya (aap key ustaad Hazrat Jaafar bin Muhammad ney (ye aayat isi tarah padhi thi : (وَاتَّخِذُوا) unhoney farmaya : haan ."
2961,ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo bimar ho gaeen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke wo sawar ho kar logon key peechey sey tawaf kar lein. unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaba ki taraf munh kar key namaz ada kar rahey they aur ye aayaat tilawat farma rahey they : ( وَالطُّوْرِ - - وَکِتَابٍ مَّسْطُوْر )' qism hai taur ki aur likhi hui kitab ki. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye abu-Bakar bin sheeba ki hadees hai.
2962,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Hazrat Shuaib bin Muhammad) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma)) key barey mein bayan kartey huye farmaya : mainey apney dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath tawaf kya. jab hum saat chakkaron sey farigh huye to hamney Kaba key peechey namaz ada ki. mainey kaha : kya aap aag sey Allah ki panah nahin maangtey ? unhoney kaha : main ( jahannam ki) aag sey Allah ki panah maangta hun . phir wo (Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) chaley aur Hajar Aswad ko bosa diya . phir Hajare-Aswad aur (kaaba key) darwazey key darmiyan khadey ho kar apna seena, apney haath aur rukhsaar Kaba sey laga diya . phir farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha hai."
2963,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath rawana huye to hamara irada sirf Haj ka tha. jab hum Sarf key maqam par ya sarf key qarib pahunchey to mujhey haiz aa gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to main ro rahi thi. aap ney farmaya : tujhey kya huwa? kya haiz aa gaya? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : ye to aisi chiz hai jo Allah Taala ney Adam (Alaihissalam) ki betiyon par likhi hai. to Haj key sarey aamal ada kar magar Baitullah ka tawaf na karna. ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon ki taraf sey gaey zibeh ki."
2964,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajje mufrad ada kiya.
2965,Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajje-mufrad ada kiya.
2966,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajje-mufrad ada kiya.
2967,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Hazrat Abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr , aur Hazrat Usman Raziallahu anhum ney Hajje-mufrad ada kiya."
2968,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Makka ki taraf rawana huye. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : (لَبَّيْكَ عُمْرَةً وَحِجَّةً), ''Umraa aur Haj key liye hazir hun.''"
2969,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( لَبَّيْكَ بِعُمْرَةٍ وَّ حَجَّةٍ ), ''aey Allah ! main umra aur Haj ki labbaik kehta hun.''"
2970,"Hazrat Sabiee bin Maabad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main eik Esai aadmi tha, phir main musalman ho gaya. mainey Haj aur Umerey key liye labbaik kaha . qaadsiya mein mujhey Hazrat Salman bin Rabeea (Rahimahullah) aur Zaid bin Sohaan (Rahimahullah) ney Haj o Umra key liye labbaik pukartey suna to kaha : ye shakhs to apney oont sey bhi ziyada kam aql hai. unhoney ye baat keh kar mujh par goya eik pahad ka bojh laad diya.) unki baat sey mujhey be inteha pareshani hui.) mainey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar ye baat batai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) un ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur sakht tanbih farmaai, phir meri taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : teri rehnumai (Allah ki taraf sey) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ki taraf ki gaee. tujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ki raah mil gaee. Hisham ney apni hadees mein kaha : raawi hadees Shaqeeq ney kaha ke main aur Masruq (Rahimahullah) aksar (Sabiee bin Maabad sey) unkey us waqiey key barey mein sawal karney key liye jatey . eik riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : main thodi der pehley hi Esai mazhab chhod kar musalman huwa tha. mainey ( ziyada sey ziyada aur behtar ibadat ki) puri puri koshish ki, chunanche mainey Haj aur Umerey ka ehraam baandha, phir mazkura baala (hadees) ki tarah bayan kya."
2971,Hazrat abu-Talha (Zaid bin Sehal Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Haj o Umra ko mila kar (hajje-Qiran) kya.
2972,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah , Hazrat Abdullah bin umr aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum jab (Makka mukarrma) tashrif laye to unhoney apney Haj aur Umerey (dono) key liye sirf eik hi tawaf kya tha."
2973,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Haj aur Umerey key liye eik hi tawaf kya.
2974,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke wo Hajje-Qiran ki niyat sey tashrif laye to Baitullah key tawaf key sath chakkar lagaey aur Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee ki, phir farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isi tarah kya tha."
2975,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Haj aur Umerey ka ikhatta ehraam baandha, usey un dono key liye eik tawaf kafi hai. aur wo ehraam nahin kholega yahan tak key Haj pura kar ley aur dono sey ikhatta ehraam kholey ."
2976,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maqame-Aqeeq par ye farmatey suna : merey paas merey rab ki taraf sey eik aaney wala aaya aur usney kaha is Mubarak wadi mein namaz ada kijiye aur kahey : Umra Haj mein dakhil hai. is riwayat key alfaz Imam Ibne-Maja key ustad Duhem (Abdur-Rehman bin Ibrahim Dimashqi) key hain."
2977,"Hazrat Suraqa bin Jasham (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is wadi mein khadey ho kar khutba diya aur farmaya : suno! Umra qiyamat tak key liye Haj mein dakhil ho gaya hai."
2978,"Hazrat Mutrif bin Abdullah bin shikhkhir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main tujhey eik hadees sunata hun, shayad aaj key baad (aainda zindagi mein) Allah us sey tujhey faeyda dey . yad rakho ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar key chand afrad ney zul-hijja key pehley ashrey mein Umra kya tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana nahin kya, na uskey mansookh honey ka hukm nazil huwa . uskey baad eik aadmi ney apni raey sey jo chah keh diya ."
2979,"Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai key wo Haj tamattoa key jawaz ka fatwa diya kartey they. unhein eik aadmi ney kaha : abhi apney kuch fatwey deney sey ijtinab kijiye. aap ko malum nahin ke aap ki ghair mojudgi mein ameerul-Momenin ney Haj key barey mein kya farmaya hai. (abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya :) main baad mein un sey mila aur daryaft kya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey malum hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aur aap key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney ye (tamatto) kya hai lekin mujhey ye baat achi na lagi ke log raat ko darakhton tuley aurton sey khilwat keren, phir subh ko Haj key liye rawana ho jaeyn jab key unkey saron sey (nahaney ki wajeh sey pani key) qatrey tapak rahey hon."
2980,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath mehaz Haj ki niyat sey (ehraam baandh kar) labbaik pukara, hamara irada uskey sath Umra milaaney ka na tha, chunaanche hum zul-hijja ki chaar raaten guzarney par (chaar taareekh ko) Makka pahunchey. jab hamney Baitullah ka tawaf kar key Safa o Marwa ki saee kar li to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen hukm diya ke hum us (tawaf aur saee) ko Umra bana den aur (ehraam khol kar) aurton sey khilwat karen. hamney aapas mein kaha : Arfa janey mein sirf paanch raaten baqi hain. to kya hum is haal mein Arfa jaeyngey ke hamarey makhsus aaza sey mani key qatrey tapak rahey hon? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tum sab sey badh kar nek aur sacha hun . agar (merey sath) qurbani key janwer na hotey to main bhi ehraam khol deta. Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya ye tamatto (ki ijazat) sirf us saal key liye hai ya hamesha key liye? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, balke hamesha hamesha key liye ."
2981,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : zul-qada ki paanch raatein baqi thin jab hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath (Madiney sey) rawana huye. hamara irada sirf Haj ka tha. jab hum chaley aur (Makka shareef key) qarib pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un logon ko ehraam kholney ka hukm dey diya jinkey sath qurbani key janwer nahin they. sab logon ney ehraam khol diya, siwaye uskey jis key paas qurbani thi . jab qurbani ka din aaya to hamarey paas gaey ka gosht laya gaya aur bataya gaya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni biwiyon ki taraf sey (gaey ki) qurbani ki hai."
2982,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum bahar hamarey paas tashrif laye . hamney Haj ka ehraam baandha . jab hum Makka aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney Haj ko Umra bana do . logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! hamney Haj ka ehraam baandha hai, usey Umra kis tarah banaeyn? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dekho! main tumhein jo hukm deta hun is par amal karo . Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney dobara wohi baat arz ki to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naraz ho kar chal diye . aap Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas tashrif laye to ( abhi tak) ghussey ki haalat mein they. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chehra aqdas par narazi key aasaar dikhey to arz kya : aapko kis ney naraz kya? Allah usey ghussey mein mubtala kar dey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main kyon naraz na hon? main eik hukm deta hon to merey hukm ki taameel nahin ki jati."
2983,"Hazrat Asma bint abi Bakr (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath ehraam baandh kar rawana huye, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jiskey paas qurbani ka janwer hai, wo ehraam baandhey rahey aur jis key paas qurbani ka janwer nahin wo halal ho jaey (ehraam khol dey). Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ney bayan farmaya : merey sath qurbani ka janwer nahin tha, isliye mainey ehraam khol diya aur (merey shohar) Hazrat Zuber key paas qurbani ka janwer tha, isliye unhoney ehraam na khola . mainey apney (aam) kapdey pehan liye aur Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) key paas chali gai. unhoney kaha : merey paas sey uth jao. mainey kaha : kya aapko ye khatra hai ke main aap par kood padungi?"
2984,"Hazrat Bilal bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! kya Haj ( ki niyat) ko faskh karkey Umra bana dena sirf hamarey liye khas hukm hai ya sab logon key liye aam hukm hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : balke khas tor par hamarey liye hai."
2985,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Haj mein tamatto karna sirf Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum key liye tha."
2986,"Hazrat Urwa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha : main is baat ko gunah nahin samajhta ke Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan chakkar na lagaaun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Allah Taala (to ye) farmata hai : ( إِنَّ الصَّفَا وَالْمَرْوَةَ مِنْ شَعَائِرِ اللَّهِ فَمَنْ حَجَّ الْبَيْتَ أَوْ اعْتَمَرَ فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْهِ أَنْ يَطَّوَّفَ بِهِمَا )' beshak Safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein sey hain, isliye Baitullah ka Haj ya Umra karney waley par unka chakkar laganey (saee kerney) mein koi harj nahin . agar wo baat durust hoti jo tum kehtey ho to (Allah ka irshad) is tarah hota : ( فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْهِ أَنْ لَا يَطَّوَّفَ بِهِمَا ) unka chakkar na laganey mein koi harj nahin. ye aayat to ansaar key baaz logon key barey mein nazil hui hai. wo jab labbaik pukartey they to Manaat (but) key naam sey labbaik pukartey they, phir (un key khayal mein) Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee karna unkey liye jayez nahin hota tha. jab wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj key liye (Makka tashreef) aaye to unhoney ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz ki, tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai. meri umr ki qasam! Allah Taala us shakhs ka Haj mukammal taslim nahin karta jo Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan chakkar na lagaey ."
2987,Hazrat Safiya binte-Shiba (Raziallahu anha) ney Hazrat Shiba (bin Usman) (Raziallahu anhu) ki Umme-walad (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat ki ke unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee kartey dekha jabkey aap farma rahey they : sangrezon wali zamin sirf daud kar hi tey ki jaey.
2988,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : agar main Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan daudun to (ye durust hai kyonkey) mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (us maqam par) dodtey dekha hai. aur agar (aam raftaar sey) chalun to (ye bhi durust hai kyonkey) mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko chaltey huye bhi dekha hai. aur main badi umr ka boodha aadmi hun (isliye daudnaa mushkil mehsus hota hai.)"
2989,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaid Allah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna , aap farma rahey they : Haj jihad hai aur Umra nafli ibadat hai."
2990,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Umra kya to hum log aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they, chunanche aap ney tawaf kya aur hamney bhi aap key sath tawaf kya. aap ney namaz padhi aur hamney bhi aap key sath namaz padhi . hum Makka walon sey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki (hifazat key liye) aad bantey they taake koi aap ko kisi qism ki guzand na pahunchaey ."
2991,"Hazrat Wahab bin Khanbash (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan main eik Umra , eik Haj key barabar hai."
2992,"Hazrat Haram bin Khanbash (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan main eik Umra , eik Haj key barabar hai."
2993,"Hazrat Abu-Ma'aqil ( haisam Ansari ( (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan main eik Umra , eik Haj key barabar hai."
2994,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan main eik Umra eik Haj key barabar hai."
2995,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ramzan main eik Umra , eik Haj key barabar hai."
2996,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney zul-qada key siwa (kisi aur mahiney mein) Umra nahin kya."
2997,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney zul-qada key siwa (kisi aur mahiney mein) Umra ada nahin farmaya."
2998,"Hazrat Urwa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey sawal kya gaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kis mahiney mein Umra kya? unhoney farmaya : Rajab mein. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kabhi Rajab mein Umra nahin kya. aur jab bhi Umra kya Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they."
2999,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein hukm diya ke Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko apney peechey sawari par bitha kar Taneem sey Umra kara den ."
3000,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath ( Madina sey) rawana huye aur zul-hijja ka chaand chadhney hi wala tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs Umerey ka ehraam baandhna chahey baandh ley. agar main qurbani na laya hota to main bhi Umerey ki niyat sey labbaik pukarta . ummul-momenin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : to logon mein sey kisi ney Umerey ka ehraam baandha , aur kisi ney Haj ka ehraam baandha. main Umerey ka ehraam baandhney walon mein shamil thi . unhoney farmaya : hum log rawana huye yahan tak ke Makka shareef pahunch gaey . abhi mein haiz sey thi ke Arfey ka din aa pahuncha. aur mainey abhi Umerey ka ehraam nahin khola tha. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey soorate-haal arz ki to aap ney farmaya : apna Umra rehney do, sar key baal khol kar kanghi kar lo, aur Haj ka ehraam baandh lo. unhoney farmaya : mainey aisey hi kya. jab hasba ki raat aai aur Allah Taala ney hamara Haj mukammal kar diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey sath Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhuma) ko bheja. wo mujhey sawari par apney peechey bitha kar tan'eem ley gaey. (aur mainey wahan sey ehraam baandh kar Umra kya.) chunanche mainey Umra kar key ehraam khol diya . is tarah Allah ney hamara Haj aur hamara Umra dono purey kar diye aur is mein na qurbani thi, na sadqa aur na rozey ."
3001,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney baitul-Maqdis sey ehraam baandh kar Umra kya, usey bakhsh diya jaeyga."
3002,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney baitul-Maqdis sey ehraam baandh kar Umra kya, wo uskey sabiqa tamam gunahon ka kaffara ho jata hai. ummul-momenin ney farmaya : chunanche mein (baitul-Maqdis sey) Umerey key liye rawana hui."
3003,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar Umerey kiye : hudebia ka umrah, agley saal umratul-qaza, teesra Jaarana sey aur chotha wo jo aap ney Haj key sath kya."
3004,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tarwiya key din (8 zul-hijja ko) zohar, Asr, maghrib, Isha aur Fajr (9 zul-hijja ko) Mina mein ada kin, phir Arfa ki taraf rawana huye."
3005,"Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) Mina mein paanch namazein padhtey they, phir logon ko batatey ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi isi tarah kartey they."
3006,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum aap key liye Mina main eik ghar na bana den ? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, Mina us shakhs key liye oont bithaaney (aur qiyam kerney) ki jagah hai jo pehley (wahan) pahunch jaey ."
3007,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! kya hum aap key liye Mina main eik ghar na bana den, jahan aap ko saya hasil ho? aap ney farmaya : nahin, Mina us shakhs key liye oont bithaaney (aur qiyam kerney) ki jagah hai jo pehley (wahan) pahunch jaey ."
3008,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath us din (9 zul-hijja ko) Mina sey Arfa ki taraf rawana huye. hum mein sey koi takbirat keh raha tha aur koi labbaik pukar raha tha. na ye is par tanqeed karta tha na wo us par. ya ye farmaya : na ye un par tanqeed kartey they, na wo un par."
3009,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Arafat mein wadi namra mein thehertey they. Hazrat Saeed bin Hassan bayan kartey hain : jab Hujjaaj ney Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhuma) ko shaheed kar diya to (uskey baad Haj key doran mein) usney aadmi bhej kar Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey daryaft kya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us din kis waqt (Arafat key maidan mein) jatey they? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : jab wo waqt aayega hum rawana ho jaeyngey (aur tumhen malum ho jaeyga.) Hujjaaj ney eik aadmi bheja ke dekhey wo kis waqt rawana hotey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney jab ( namra sey) rawana honey ka irada kya to farmaya : kya suraj dhal gaya hai? logon ney kaha : abhi nahin dhala. aap beth gaey. (kuch der baad) phir kaha : kya suraj dhal gaya hai? logon ney kaha : abhi nahin dhala. aap beth gaey. (kuch der baad) phir kaha : kya suraj dhal gaya hai? logon ney kaha : abhi nahin dhala. aap beth gaey. (kuch der baad) phir kaha : kya suraj dhal gaya hai? logon ney kaha : ji haan. jab unhoney kaha : dhal gaya hai, tab Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) rawana huye."
3010,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Arafat mein thehrey to farmaya : ye theherney ki jagah hai. aur Arafat sab key theherney ki jagah hai."
3011,"Hazrat Yazeed bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik jagah thehrey huye they jisey aap theherney ki jagah sey door hi qarar dey saktey hain. Hazrat ibn Mirbaa (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaye aur kaha : main tumharey paas Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka pegham laya hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey hain : apney apney maqam par thehrey raho. aaj tum Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki eik virasat key hamil ho."
3012,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Arafat sab ka sab theherney ki jagah hai, albatta Arna key nashebi hissey sey ooper raho. Muzdalfa sabka sab theherney ki jagah hai, albatta wadiye Muhassir ki nasheb sey ooper raho. Mina sab ka sab qurbani ki jagah hai, siwaye uskey jo ghaati key peechey hai."
3013,"Hazrat Abbas bin Mirdas Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Arafat key din ( wuqoof key doran mein) apni ummat ki bakhshish key liye dua farmaai. (Allah ki taraf sey) aap ko jawab diya gaya : mainey unhein bakhsh diya siwaye zalim key, ke main us sey mazloom ka haq wasul karunga . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya rab ! agar to chahey to mazloom ko jannat sey (uski mazlumiyat key badley mein nematein) dey dey, aur zalim ko maaf kar dey. us din aap ki dua qubul na hui. subh ko jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Muzdalfa mein they, aap ney dobara dua ki to aap ki dua qubul ho gaee . Raavi bayan farmatey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans padey ya muskura diye . Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney arz kya : merey maa-baap aap par qurban! aisey waqt aap hansa nahin kartey they to (aaj) aap kis liye hansey hain? Allah aap key daanton ko hansta rakhey! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key dushman iblees ko jab malum huwa ke Allah ney meri dua qubul farma li hai aur meri ummat ko maaf kar diya hai to usney khaak ley kar apney sar par dalna shuru kar di aur chalaney laga : haaye meri tabahi ! haaye kharabi ! uski pareshani (aur ronaa peetna) dekh kar mujhey hansi aa gaee ."
3014,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah azz-w-jall Arfa key din sey ziyada kisi aur din bandon ko aag sey azad nahin karta. Allah azz-w-jall (bandon sey) qarib hota hai, phir aur qarib hota hai, phir un ki wajeh sey farishton key samney izhar fakhr farmata hai aur kehta hai : ye log kya chahtey hain?"
3015,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamar Deli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa jabke aap Arafat mein thehrey huye they. aap ki khidmat mein Najad key kuch afrad hazir huye aur unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Haj ka kya tariqa hai? aap ney farmaya : Haj to Arfa hi (ka naam) hai. jo shakhs Muzdalfa ki raat ko Fajr ki namaz sey pehley aa gaya, uska Haj pura ho gaya, Mina key din teen hain, phir jo shakhs do dino mein jaldi sey (wapis) chala jaey, is par gunah nahin aur jo takheer karey (teesra din bhi wuqoof kerey), is par bhi koi gunah nahin. phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney peechey eik aadmi ko (sawari par) bitha liya aur usney un masaayel ka aelan karna shuru kar diya . Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Muhammad bin yahyaa key tareeq sey bhi ye riwayat sabiqa hadees key hum-maana zikr ki hai lekin is mein ( شَهِدْتُ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ , وَهُوَ وَاقِفٌ بِعَرَفَةَ , وَأَتَاهُ نَاسٌ مِنْ أَهْلِ نَجْدٍ ) ki bajaey ( أَتَيْتُ رَسُولَ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ بِعَرَفَةَ , فَجَاءَهُ نَفَرٌ مِنْ أَهْلِ نَجْدٍ ) key alfaz zikr kiye hain. ( mafhoom dono ibaraton ka eik hi hai. ( Raavi hadees Muhammad bin yahyaa ney kaha : merey nazdik Sufiyan Sory ki us sey behtar aur koi hadees nahin ."
3016,"Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris Taai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein Haj kya. wo (aam) logon tak us waqt pahunchey jab log Muzdalfa mein they. wo kehtey hain : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! mainey apni sawari ko (taweel safar kar key) dubla kar diya aur apni jaan ko thaka diya. qism hai Allah ki! mainey koi tila nahin chhoda jis par thehra na hun. to kya mera Haj ho gaya? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hamarey sath (Muzdalfa mein Fajr ki) namaz mein mila aur wo is sey pehley raat ko ya din ko Arafat sey ho aaya hai, usney apna mail kuchail door kar liya aur uska Haj pura ho gaya ."
3017,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, un sey sawal kya gaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Arafat sey rawana hotey they to kis tarah chaltey they? unhoney farmaya : darmiyani raftaar sey chaltey they. jab khuli jagah milti to raftaar tez kar detey. hadees key raawi Wakee (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : yani aap darmiyani raftaar sey thoda sa tez chaltey ."
3018,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Quraish kehtey they : hum Baitullah key paas rehney waley hain. hum Haram (ki hadon) sey aagey nahin jaeyngey, isliye Allah Taala ney farmaya : ( ثُمَّ أَفِيضُوا مِنْ حَيْثُ أَفَاضَ النَّاسُ )' phir wahan sey wapis aao jahan sey (doosrey) log wapis ayen."
3019,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath (Arafat sey) wapis huwa. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us ghaati key paas pahunchey jiskey paas ameer qiyam kartey hain, aap sawari sey utrey aur peshab kya, phir aap ney wuzu kya. mainey kaha : namaz! farmaya : namaz aagey hogi. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Muzdalfa pahunchey to Azan aur iqaamat kahlwaai, phir maghrib ki namaz padhaai, phir kisi ney bhi oonton sey saman nahin utara tha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth khadey huye aur Isha ki namaz padhaai."
3020,"Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey hajjatul-wada mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath maghrib aur Isha ki namazein Muzdalfa mein ada kin ."
3021,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Muzdalfa mein maghrib ki namaz ada ki. jab hamney apney oont bithaaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz iqaamat key sath hoti hai.
3022,"Hazrat Amr bin Memun (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hamney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Haj kya. jab hum Muzdalfa sey wapis honey lagey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mushrekin kaha kartey they : aey Sabeer pahad! roshan ho ja taake hum (wapis Mina ki taraf) bhagen . wo us waqt tak wapis nahin laut'tey they jab tak ke suraj tulu na ho jata . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey khilaf amal kya ke suraj tulu honey sey pehley wapis chal diye ."
3023,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hajjatul-wadaa mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( Muzdalfa sey) wapis lotey to aap par itminan o sukoon ki keyfiyat thi . aap ney logon ko bhi sukoon ka hukm diya . aur unhein aisi ( chhoti) kankariyon key sath rami karney ka hukm diya jo ungliyon mein pakad kar phenki ja saken . aap ney wadiye Muhassir mein sawari ko tez kya aur farmaya : meri ummat ko chahiye ke apney ibadat key tareeqey seekh ley . mujhey malum nahin shayad mein us saal key baad un sey (hajj mein) mulaqat na kar sakun."
3024,"Hazrat Bilal bin Ribah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Muzdalfa ki subh un sey farmaya : Bilaal! logon ko khamosh karo. phir farmaya : Allah Taala ney tumharey us Muzdalfa main tum par ehsan farmaya hai ke tumharey nekukaron ki wajeh sey tumharey gunahgaaron ko bhi bakhsh diya hai aur tumharey nekukaron ney jo kuch manga unhein dey diya. Allah ka naam ley kar rawana ho jao ."
3025,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Abdul-Muttalib key khandan key chand ladkey Muzdalfa sey apni gadhiyon par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey pehley rawana ho gaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari raanon par haath maar kar farmaya : merey piyarey beto! us waqt tak jamre par kankariyaan na maarna jab tak suraj tulu na ho jaey.(hadees key raawi) Sufiyan ney mazkura riwayat mein un alfaz ka izafa kya hai : merey khayal mein koi bhi suraj tulu honey sey pehley usey rami nahin kerega ."
3026,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney ghar key jo kamzor afrad (aurten aur bachey, quwat waley logon sey) pehley (Muzdalfa sey Mina) bhejey they, main bhi un mein shamil tha."
3027,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke ummul-momenin Hazrat Sauda binte-Zama (Raziallahu anha) bhari badan wali khatoon thin . unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ijazat chahi ke Muzdalfa sey logon key rawana honey sey pehley rawana ho jaeyn, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein ijazat dey di."
3028,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Amr bin ahwas (Rahimahullah) apni walida (Hazrat Umme Jundub Azdiya (Raziallahu anha)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey qurbani key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Jamrae-Aqba (badey jamre) key paas dekha jabke aap khachar par sawar they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logo ! jab tum jamre par kankariyaan maaro to chhoti kankariyaan maaro ."
3029,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Jamrae-Aqba ko Rami karney key din subh key waqt Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni oontni par sawar they, tab aap ney farmaya : mujhey kankariyaan chun do. mainey aap ko saat kankariyaan chun din, jo ungliyon mein pakad kar phainkney key qabil thin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhein apney haath mein ley kar harkat deney lagey aur farmaya : un jaisi kankariyaan maaro. phir farmaya : logo! Deen mein ghulw (aur had sey badhney) sey perhez karo. tum sey pehley logon ko Deen mein ghulw hi ney tabah kya hai."
3030,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) jab Jamarae-Aqba key paas aaye to wadi key nashebi hissey mein chaley gaey, Kaba ki taraf munh kya, jamre ko apney daain abru key muqabil rakha aur saat kankariyaan maarin. har kankari key sath Allahu-akbar kehtey they, phir farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key siwa koi mabood nahin, usi jagah khadey ho kar kankariyan maari thin us shakhsiyat ney jin par sura Baqra nazil hui."
3031,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Amr bin ahwas (Raziallahu anhu) apni walida (Hazrat Umme Jundub (Raziallahu anha)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : mainey qurbani key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Jamarae-Aqba ( badey jamre) key paas dekha. aap wadi key nashebi hissey mein chaley gaey aur jamre ko saat kankariyaan maarin. har kankari key sath takbir ( Allahu-akbar) kehtey they, phir wapis tashrif ley gaey. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey bhi ye riwayat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sabiqa hadees key hum maana bayan ki hai."
3032,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Jamrae-Aqba ko kankariyaan maarin aur uskey paas na rukey aur bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi isi tarah kya tha.
3033,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Jamrae-Aqba (badey jamre) ko rami kartey to chaltey jatey they, thehertey nahin they."
3034,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni sawari par (sawar ho kar) jamre ko kankariyaan maarin.
3035,"Hazrat Qudama bin Abdullah Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey qurbani key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney jamre ko rami ki. aap apni eik surkh o safed rang ki oontni par sawar they. na kisi ko maara jata tha, na door hataaya jata tha, aur na hato bacho ki aawazen thin ."
3036,Hazrat Abu-Badaah Adi bin Aasim (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Aasim bin Adi bin Jad (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney charwaahon ko ijazat di ke wo eik din rami karen aur eik din chhod den.
3037,"Hazrat Abu-Badaah Adi bin Aasim (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Aasim bin Adi bin Jad (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney oonton key charwaahon ko raat guzarney key barey mein riayat di ke wo qurbani key din rami keren, phir qurbani key baad key do din ki rami ikhatti kisi eik din (giyara ya baara taareekh ko) kar lein. Imam Malik ney farmaya : mera khayal hai ke Raavi ney ye kaha tha : do dino mein sey pehley din (giyara zul-hijja ko) rami kar lein. uskey baad wapsi key din (tera zul-hijja ko) rami kar lein."
3038,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj kya aur hamarey sath aurten aur bachey bhi they. hamney bachon ki taraf sey labbaik kaha aur un ki taraf sey rami bhi ki."
3039,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) labbaik pukartey rahey yahan tak key Jamrae-Aqba ko rami ki.
3040,"Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main sawari par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechey sawar tha, chunanche main aap ko labbaik pukartey sunta raha yahan tak key aap ney Jamrae-Aqba ( badey jamre) ko kankariyaan maarin. jab aap ney uski rami kar li to labbaik pukarna band kar diya ."
3041,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab tum Jamrae-Aqba par kankariyaan maar lo to tumharey liye aurton key siwa har chiz halal ho gaee. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey ibne-Abbas! khushbu bhi? unhoney farmaya : mainey (us moqey par) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke apney sar Mubarak ko kastoori lagatey they. to kya wo khushbu hai ya nahin ?"
3042,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ehraam key liye khushbu lagai jab aap ney ehraam baandha aur ehraam kholney par khushbu lagai jab aap ney ehraam khola ."
3043,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon ki bakhshish farma . Sahaba ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! baal katwaaney walon ki bhi . aap ney farmaya : aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon ki bakhshish farma . teen baar isi tarah dua farmaai. (teesri baar bhi) Sahaba ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! baal katwaaney walon ki bhi (bakhshish ki dua farmaiye) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aur baal katwaaney walon ki bhi (bakhshish farma.)"
3044,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah sar mundwaaney walon par rehmat farma. Sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! baal katwaaney walon par bhi . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah sar mundwaaney walon par rehmat farma. Sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! baal katwaaney walon par bhi . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah sar mundwaaney walon par rehmat farma. Sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! baal katwaaney walon par bhi . farmaya : aur baal katwaaney walon par bhi ."
3045,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke arz kya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney sar key baal mundwaaney walon ki teen baar taeed farmaai aur katwaaney walon ki eik baar ? aap ney farmaya : unhoney shak nahin kya.
3046,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya wajeh hai ke logon ney ehraam khol diya aur aap ney Umra kar key ehraam nahin khola ? aap ney farmaya : mainey sar key baalon ko jamaya huwa hai aur qurbani key janwer ko qaladey pahnaaey huye hain, isliye mein qurbani karney tak ehraam nahin kholunga."
3047,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sar key baal jamaey labbaik pukartey suna."
3048,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mina sab ka sab qurbani ki jagah hai. aur Makka ka har raasta (yahan aaney ki) raah bhi hai aur qurbani ki jagah bhi. aur pura Arafat theherney ki jagah hai. aur pura Muzdalfa theherney ki jagah hai."
3049,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey jis shakhs key barey mein bhi sawal kya gaya ke usney eik kaam sey pehley doosra kaam kar liya hai, ( to uskey jawab mein) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dono haathon sey ishara kar key yehi farmaya : koi harj nahin ."
3050,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Mina key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawalat kiye jatey they to aap farmatey they : koi harj nahin, koi harj nahin . eik shakhs ney aa kar kaha : mainey zibeh karney sey pehley sar mundwaa liya hai. aap ney farmaya : koi harj nahin . kisi ney arz kya : mainey Sham honey par rami ki hai. aap ney farmaya : koi harj nahin ."
3051,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya ke kisi ney sar mundwaaney sey pehley zibeh kar liya , ya zibeh karney sey pehley sar mundwa liya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi harj nahin ."
3052,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qurbani key din Mina mein logon (ko masaayel bataaney) key liye beth gaey. eik aadmi ney aa kar kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey zibeh karney sey pehley sar mundwaa liya. aap ney farmaya : koi harj nahin. phir eik aur aadmi aaya, usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey rami (kankar maarney) sey pehley janwer ki qurbani dey di. aap ney farmaya : koi harj nahin. us din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey jis kaam key barey mein bhi sawal kiya gaya jisey doosrey kaam sey pehley kar liya gaya tha, aap ney yehi farmaya : koi harj nahin."
3053,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (das taareekh ko) badey jamre ko chaasht key waqt (dhoop chadhey) rami ki. uskey baad key dino mein suraj dhalney key baad rami ki."
3054,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) suraj dhalney sey itni der baad jamaraat par kankariyaan maartay they ke jab rami sey farigh hotey to Zohar ki namaz padh letey.
3055,"Hazrat Amr bin Ahwas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hajjatul-wadaa mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : aey logo ! kon sa din ziyada hurmat (aur ehtiraam) wala hai? teen baar farmaya : haazirin ney kaha : Haje-Akbar ka din. aap ney farmaya : tumharey khoon, tumharey maal, tumhari izzatein eik doosrey key liye isi tarah qabile-ehtiraam hain jis tarah tumharey is shehar (Makka Mukarrma) mein, tumharey is mahiney (zul-hijja) ka ye din qabile ehtiraam hai. suno ! mujrim key jurm ki zimme-daari sirf usi par hai. baap key jurm ki zimme-daari uskey betey par nahin aur betey key jurm ki zimme-daari uskey baap par nahin. suno ! shetan is baat sey mayus ho chuka hai ke tumharey is shehar mein kabhi uski puja ki jaey, lekin baaz aisey kamon mein uski itaat hoti rahegi jinhein tum maamuli samajhtey ho, aur wo is par razi ho jaeyga. suno ! jahiliyat mein kya janey wala har khoon kal-adam (muaaf) hai. sab sey pehley main Haris bin Abdul-Muttalib ka khoon maaf karta hun. ye (doodh peene wala bachcha) qabila banu Les mein parwarish paa raha tha. banu Huzail ney isey qatl kar diya . suno ! jahiliyat ka har sood kal-adam (muaaf) hai, sirf asal zar tumhara haq hai, na tum zulm karo, na tum par zulm kiya jaey. suno ! meri ummat ! kya mainey (Allah key ehkam) pahuncha diye? teen baar farmaya : sab ney kaha : ji haan. tab aap ney teen baar farmaya : aey Allah ! gawah reh."
3056,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Mina mein maqame khaif par khadey huye aur farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs ko tar-o-taza rakhey jo meri baat suney aur usey (doosron tak) pahuncha dey. baaz logon key paas fiq'h ki baat hoti hai aur wo khud faqeeh nahin hotey. baaz log fiq'h ki baat apney sey ziyada faqeeh tak pahuncha detey hain. teen kamon mein momin ka dil khayanat nahin karta : amal ko Allah key liye khulus key sath ada karna, musalman hukmranon ki khair-khahi karna aur un ki ijtimaaiyat mein shamil rehna kyonkey un ki dua dusron ko bhi shamil hoti hai."
3057,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Arafat main apni kaan kati oontni par sawar they. us waqt aap ney farmaya : kya tumhen malum hai ke ye kon sa din, kon sa mahina aur kon sa shehar hai? Sahaba ney arz kiya : ye hurmat wala shehar, hurmat wala mahina aur hurmat wala din hai. aap ney farmaya : suno ! haqiqat ye hai ke tumharey maal aur tumharey khoon tumharey liye (eik doosrey key liye) isi tarah qabile-ehtiraam hain jis tarah tumharey is shehar (Makka Mukarrma) mein, tumharey is (Hajj key) din main tumhara mahina qabile-ehtiraam hai. suno ! main hoz (kausar) par tumhara peshrau hunga aur tumhari kasrate-tadaad ki wajeh sey dusri qomon par fakhr karunga to mujhey (qiyamat key din) ruswa na kar dena. suno ! main kuch afrad ko (jahannam sey) chhudaaoonga aur kuch log mujh sey chheen liye jaeyngey (aur jahannam mein bhej diye jaeyngey). main kahunga : merey Rab ! merey sathi? to Allah Taala farmaeyga : aap ko nahin maloom, unhoney aap key baad kya naey kaam kiye."
3058,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jo Haj ada farmaya , us Haj key moqey par qurbani key din jamaraat key darmiyan khadey huye. (us waqt) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye kon sa din hai? logon ney kaha : qurbani ka din hai. aap ney farmaya : ye kon sa shehar hai? unhoney kaha : ye Allah ka hurmat wala shehar hai. aap ney farmaya ye kon sa mahina hai? unhoney kaha : ye Allah ka hurmat wala mahina hai. aap ney farmaya : ye Hajje-Akbar ka din hai aur tumhari janen, tumharey maal, tumhari izzatein eik doosrey key liye isi tarah qabile-ehtiraam hain jis tarah is mahiney key is din mein is shehar ka ehtiraam hai. phir farmaya : kya mainey pahuncha diya? logon ney kaha : ji haan. tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! gawah reh. phir logon ko alwidaa kaha. Sahaba ney kaha : ye Hajjatul-wadaa, yani alwadaai Haj hai."
3059,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tawaafe-ziyaarat raat tak muakhkhar farmaya (deri ki).
3060,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tawafe-ifaaza key saat chakkaron mein ramal nahin kiya. Janab Ata (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : is (tawaf) mein ramal nahin hota.
3061,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) key paas betha huwa tha ke eik aadmi unkey paas aaya. unhoney puchha : kahan sey aaye ho? usney kaha : zamzam sey. farmaya : kya tum ney is mein sey is tarah piya hai jis tarah peena chahiye ? usney kaha : wo kis tarah hai? farmaya : jab to us (chahe-zamzam) sey pani piye to qibley ki taraf munh kar, Allah ka naam ley, teen saans ley aur sair ho kar pi. jab to pi chukey to Allah ka shukar ada kar kyonkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : hamarey aur munafiqon key darmiyan (pehchan key liye) ye alamat hai ke wo zamzam sair ho kar nahin peetey."
3062,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zamzam ka pani is (maqsad) key liye hai jis key liye wo piya jaey."
3063,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Fateh Makka key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaabae-Shareef mein dakhil huye aur aap key sath Hazrat Bilal aur Hazrat Usman bin sheeba (Raziallahu anhuma) they. unhoney andar sey Kaabey ka darwaza band kar liya . jab wo bahar nikley to mainey Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kahan namaz padhi thi? unhoney mujhey bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dakhil honey key baad samney key rukh daain taraf key do sutonon key darmiyan namaz padhi thi. baad mein mainey khud ko malamat ki ke mainey ye kyon na poochh liya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kitni namaz padhi thi?"
3064,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas sey bahar tashrif ley gaey to aap mutmain aur khush they. phir merey paas wapis aaey to ghamgin they. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap merey paas sey tashrif ley gaey to aap mutmain aur khush they aur wapis aaye to aap ghamgin (aur pareshan) hain (iski kya wajeh hai)? aap ney farmaya : main Kaabey key andar gaya tha. ab mera ji chahta hai ke (kaash) mainey aisey na kiya hota. mujhey khadsha (dar) hai ke (apney is amal ki wajeh sey) apney baad apni ummat ko mashaqqat mein mubtala na kar dun."
3065,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ney pani pilaney key farize ki adaegi key liye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ijazat chahi ke Mina key dinon mein raat ko Makka mein rahen, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein ijazat dey di."
3066,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi (Haaji) ko Makka mein raat guzarney ki ijazat nahin di, siwaye Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key, (jinhein) unkey paani pilaane ke pad ki wajeh sey (raat ko Makka mein rehney ki ijazat di)."
3067,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : maidan abtah mein theharna koi sunnat (aur sharaee hukm) nahin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan sirf isliye thehrey they ke (wahan sey) rawangi mein aap key liye aasani thi."
3068,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapsi ki raat Bat'haa sey raat key aakhiri hissey mein rawana huye."
3069,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman Raziallahu anhum abtah key maqam par qiyam farmatey they."
3070,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : log (Haj key aamaal sey farigh ho kar Mina hi sey) har taraf wapis (apney apney watan ko) chaley jatey they, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs kooch na karey jab tak wo (rawangi sey pehley) aakhiri waqt Baitullah key paas (tawaf mein) na guzaarey."
3071,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aakhiri waqt tawafe-Baitullah kiye baghair (wapis) kooch karney sey mana farmaya."
3072,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Safiya binte Huyi (Raziallahu anha) ko tawaafe-ifaaza key baad haiz shuru ho gaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmaati hain : mainey ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya wo hamein (rawaangi sey) rok degi? mainey kaha : usney tawaafe-ifaaza kar liya tha, uskey baad haiz shuru huwa hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir wo rawana ho sakti hai."
3073,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ko yad farmaya : hamney arz kiya : wo dinon sey hain. aap ney farmaya : baanjh ho ! sir mundaa jaey ! main samajhta hun wo hamein (kooch karney sey) rok leygi. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! usney qurbani key din tawaaf (ifaaza) kar liya tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tab (koi rukawat) nahin, usey hukm do ke kooch karey."
3074,"Hazrat Jaafar (Saadiq) (Rahimahullah) apney walid Muhammad (Baqar) (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : hum log Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. jab hum aap key paas pahunchey to aap ney tamam afrad key barey mein puchha (ke aap log kon kon hain)? yahan tak key meri baari aa gaee. mainey kaha : main Muhammad bin Ali bin Husain hun. unhoney merey sar ki taraf haath badha kar mera ooper wala batan khola, phir (us sey) nichey wala batan khola, phir apna haath merey seeney par rakh diya. us waqt main eik jawan ladka tha. aap ney farmaya : tumhein khush aamadeed ! jo chaho poochho, chunanche mainey aap sey sawalat kiye (unhoney jawab diye). aap us waqt na-bina ho chukey they. (itney mein) namaz ka waqt ho gaya. aap eik kapda odhey huye they jo itna chhota tha ke jab usey kandhon par daltey to uskey dono kinarey aagey aa jatey (bakal maarna mushkil tha). aur un ki badi chadar unkey qarib tipaai par padi hui thi. aap ney hamein namaz padhaai. (namaz key baad) mainey kaha : hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Haj key barey mein bataaiye. aap ney haath sey nau ka ishara kar key farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (hijrat key baad Madiney mein) nau saal iqaamat-pazeer rahey aur Haj nahin kiya. daswen saal aap ney logon mein aelan karwa diya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Haj karney waley hain, chunanche Madina mein bahut sey log (aas-paas se) aagey. har eik ki yehi khahish thi ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) (mein Haj) karey aur wohi kaam karey jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) karen. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rawana huye aur hum bhi aap key sath rawana huye. hum Zul-Hulefa pahunchey to Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) key yahan Muhammad bin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhuma) ki wiladat ho gaee. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf aadmi bhej kar daryaft kiya : main kya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghusl kar key eik kapda langot ki tarah baandh ley aur ehraam baandh ley. (zul-haleefa ki) masjid mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz padhi phir qaswaa (oontni) par sawar huye. jab oontni Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ley kar bedaa (maidan) mein pahunchi to Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key aagey jahan tak meri nazar kaam karti thi sawar aur pedal afrad nazar aaye, isi tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key daain taraf (be shumar log they). aur isi tarah baain taraf, isi tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey (nazar ki had tak log they). Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey darmiyan mojud they, aap par Quran Majeed nazil hota tha aur aap uska matlab jantey they. jo kaam bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kartey they, hum bhi kartey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tohid ki aawaz buland ki : (لبيك اللهم لبيك لبيك لا شريك لك لبيك ان الحمد والنعمة لك والملك لا شریك لك), ''hazir hun, aey Allah ! hazir hun, hazir hun, tera koi shareek nahin, hazir hun, tareefen aur nematen teri hain aur badshahi bhi, tera koi shareek nahin.'' logon ney bhi in alfaz mein labbaik pukara jin alfaz mein (aaj kal) pukartey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is mein sey kisi lafz sey mana nahin kiya, albatta khud Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna (mazkoora baala) talbiya hi pukartey rahey. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hamari niyat sirf Haj ki thi, hamein Umerey ka ilm hi na tha (ke Haj key sath hi umra bhi kiya ja sakta hai) yahan tak key jab hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Kaba key paas pahunchey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajare-Aswad ka istilaam kiya (bosa liya). (tawaf key) teen chakkaron mein ramal kiya aur chaar chakkaron mein (aam raftaar sey) chaley, phir Maqame-Ibrahim par tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : (وَاتَّخِذُوْا مِن مَّقَامِ إِبْرَاهَيْمَ مُصَلي),''Maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz ki jagah banao.'' aap ney Maqame-Ibrahim ko apney aur Kaba key darmiyan kiya (aur do rakatein padhein). Imam Jaafar farmatey hain :  merey walid (Muhammad bin Ali) ka bayan hai aur yaqinan Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi sey unhoney bayan kiya hoga ke aap ney do rakaaton mein (قُلْ يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ) aur (قُلْ هُوَ ٱللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) padhi. phir dobara Baitullah ki taraf tashrif ley gaey aur Hajare-Aswad ka bosa liya, phir darwazey sey nikal kar Safa ki taraf chaley. jab Safa key qarib pahunchey to ye aayat padhi (إِنَّ ٱلصَّفَا وَٱلْمَرْوَةَ مِن شَعَآئِرِٱللَّهِ),''Safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein sey hain.'' (aur farmaya : ) hum usi sey shuru kartey hain jis ka naam Allah ney pehley liya hai. chunanche aap ney Safa sey ibtida (shuruat) ki. aap us (Safa) par chadhey yahan tak key Baitullah par nazar padi. Allah ki takbir aur tahleel aur hamd farmaai (الله اكبر، لا اله الا الله اور الحمدلله) phir farmaya : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ يُحْيِي وَيُمِيتُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ , لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , أَنْجَزَ وَعْدَهُ , وَنَصَرَ عَبْدَهُ وَهَزَمَ الْأَحْزَابَ وَحْدَهُ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, usi ki badshahi hai, aur usi ki tareefen hain, wo zinda karta aur maut deta hai aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai. akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. uska koi shareek nahin, usney apna wada pura kiya, apney bandey ki madad ki aur usi eik (haqeeqi maabud) ney (dushmanon ki sab) jamaaton ko shikast di.'' phir in (alfaz ko pehli baar aur dusri baar padhney) key darmiyan dua maangi. teen baar aisey hi kiya. phir utar kar Marwa ki taraf chaley yahan tak key jab aap key qadam nasheb (dhalaan) mein pahunchey to wadi key nashebi (dhalaan waale) hissey mein daudey, phir jab (aap key qadam) buland jagah pahunchey to aap (aam raftaar sey) chal kar Marwa par pahunchey. Marwa par bhi isi tarah kiya (takbir aur tahmeed aur tahleel key baad)  لا اله الا الله وحده . . . . padha, jis tarah Safa par kiya tha (isi tarah saee puri ki). jab Marwa par aap key chakkar purey huye to farmaya : agar mujhey apney mamley key barey mein pehley wo baat malum hoti jo baad mein malum hui to main qurbani key janwer sath na lata aur is (tawaf aur saee) ko Umra bana deta, lihaza tum mein sey jis key sath hudi (qurbani ka janwer) nahin, usey chahiye ke ehraam khol dey aur usey umra bana ley. chunanche sab logon ney ehraam khol diye aur baal katwaa liye, siwaye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key aur un logon key jinkey sath qurbani key janwer they. Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) ney uth kar kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya ye hukm isi saal key liye hai ya hamesha hamesha key liye? Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dalin aur do baar farmaya : umra Haj mein is tarah dakhil ho gaya hai. (sirf is saal key liye) nahin balke hamesha hamesha key liye. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) (Yamen sey) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key oont (qurbani key liye) leykar hazir huye to dekha ke Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) bhi un afrad mein shamil hain jinhoney ehraam khol diya hai aur unhoney rang daar kapdey pehan rakhey hain aur surma lagaya huwa hai. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney unkey is kaam par naapasandeedgi ka izhar kiya to unhoney farmaya : mujhey abba jaan ney ye hukm diya hai. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Iraaq mein (ye waqia bayan kartey huye) farmaya kartey they : main Fatima (Raziallahu anha) key us amal ki shikayat karney aur unhoney jo baat batai thi uskey barey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey fatwa poochhney key liye aap ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur mainey unkey us kaam par naa-pasandeedgi ka izhar kiya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo sach kehti hai, wo sach kehti hai. tum ney jab Haj ka ehraam baandha tha to kya kaha tha? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey kaha tha : aey Allah ! main usi chiz ka ehraam baandhta hun jis ka ehraam terey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney baandha hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey sath to qurbani hai, lihaza tum bhi ehraam na kholo. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : qurbani key wo janwer jo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen sey laye they aur wo janwer jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina sey laye they, un ki majmui tadaad sau thi. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key siwa , aur jinkey sath qurbani key janwer they unkey siwa sab logon ney ehraam khol diya aur baal katwaa liye. phir jab tarwiya ka din (8 zul-hijja) aaya aur log Mina ki taraf chaley, tab unhoney Haj ka ehraam baandha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi sawar huye (aur Mina ja pahunchey) aur aap ney Mina mein Zohar , Asr , Maghrib , Isha aur Fajr ki namazein padhein, phir (Fajr ki namaz key baad) kuchh der thehrey rahey yahan tak key suraj nikal aaya. aur aap key hukm sey namra maqam mein aap key liye baalon ka (bakriyon key baalon sey bana huwa) eik khema laga diya gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Mina sey) rawana huye to Quraish ko yaqin tha ke aap Mashare-Haram ya Muzdalfa mein ruk jaeyngey, jaisey zamanae-jahiliyat mein Quraish kiya kartey they lekin Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aagey badh gaey yahan tak key Arafat mein pahunch gaey. aap ko namra mein khema laga huwa mila. aap wahan tashrif farma huye. jab suraj dhal gaya to aap key hukm sey (aap ki oontni) qaswaa par kajaawa kasa gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is par sawar ho kar wadi key nasheb (dhalaan) mein tashrif ley aaye. (wahan) logon sey khitab farmaya. (us mein) farmaya : tumharey khoon aur tumharey maal eik doosrey key liye isi tarah qabile-ehtiraam hain jis tarah tumharey is shehar (Makka) mein is mahiney (zul-hijja) ka ye (Haj ka) din. suno ! jaahili riwaaj ki har chiz merey in qadmon tuley rondi gaee. daure-jahiliyat mein ho jaaney waley qatl sab maaf hain (un ka badla nahin liya jaeyga). aur sab sey pehley main Rabeea bin Haris ka khoon maaf karta hun . ye (doodh peeta bachcha) qabila bani Saad mein parwarish paa raha tha aur qabila bin Huzail ney isey qatl kar diya tha. zamanae-jahiliyat key sab sood maaf hain. aur sab sey pehley main apney khandan ka, yani Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ka sood maaf karta hun. wo sab ka sab maaf hai. aurton key barey mein Allah sey daro. tum ney unhen Allah ki zimme-daari par hasil kiya hai aur Allah key naam par un ki ismat ko apney liye halal kiya hai. un par tumhara ye haq hai ke tumharey bistar par kisi aisey shakhs ko na bethney den jo tumhen napasand hai. agar wo ye harkat karen to unhen maaro lekin sakht maar na ho. aur tum par unka ye haq hai ke munasib andaz sey unhen khurak aur libas mohaiyya karo. aur mainey tumharey andar wo chiz chhodi hai ke agar usey mazbooti sey pakdey rahogey to hergiz gumrah nahin hogey. wo Allah ki kitab hai. aur tum sey (qiyamat key din) merey barey mein puchha jaeyga to tum kya kahogey? haazirin ney arz kiya : hum gawahi dengey ke aap ney (pura deen) pahuncha diya, (apna farz puri tarah) ada kar diya, aur (ummat ki) khair-khahi ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney shahadat ki ungli aasman ki taraf buland ki aur logon ki taraf jhukaai aur teen baar farmaya : aey Allah ! gawah reh ! aey Allah gawah reh !  uskey baad Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney Azan di, phir iqaamat kahi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai, phir ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney) iqaamat kahi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Asr ki namaz padhaai. dono namazon key darmiyan aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney koi (sunnat ya nafl) namaz ada nahin farmaai. uskey baad Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sawar ho kar (Arafat mein) wuqoof key maqam par tashrif ley gaey. aap ney chattano ki taraf apni oontni ka pet (aur pehlu) kya, aur hable-mashaat (tiley) ko apney samney kiya aur qibley ki taraf munh kiya (aur zikr aur dua mein mashghool ho gaey). aap barabar wahan thehrey rahey yahan tak key suraj ghurub ho gaya aur thodi si surkhi bhi kam ho gaee. jab suraj ki tikiyaa nazron sey bilkul ojhal ho gaee to aap ney sawari par Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) ko apney peechhey sawar kar liya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Arafat sey) rawana huye to aap ney qaswaa ki mahaar (nakel) bahut ziyada khinch rakhi thi yahan tak key uska sar aap key kajawey ki agli lakdi sey ja laga. aap daain haath sey ishara kar key farma rahey they : aey logo ! aaram sey chalo. aaram sey chalo. jab raastey mein koi teela aata to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) oontni ki mahaar dheeli chhod detey taake wo (tiley par aasani sey) chadh jaey. phir aap Muzdalfa tashrif laye. wahan eik Azan aur do iqaamaton key sath Maghrib aur Isha ki namazein ada kin. aur unkey darmiyan koi (sunnat ya nafl) namaz nahin padhi. phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) let gaey yahan tak key subah saadiq ho gaee. jab wazeh tor par subah tulu ho gaee to aap ney Azan aur iqaamat kehlwaa kar Fajr ki namaz ada ki, phir (namaz key baad) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qaswaa par sawar ho kar Mashare-Haram tashrif ley gaey. aap uskey ooper tashrif ley gaey aur Allah ki hamd aur takbir aur tahleel mein mashghool ho gaey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yahan thehrey rahey yahan tak key khub roshni ho gaee, phir suraj tulu honey sey pehley yahan sey rawana ho gaey. aap ney apney peechhey (oontni par) Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ko sawar kiya. wo khoobsurat baalon waley, gorey chittey aur khush shakal aadmi they. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) rawana huye to kuchh aurten (oonton par sawar) tezi key sath paas sey guzrin, Hazrat Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) unhen dekhney lagey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath sey (un ka chehra) dusri taraf kar diya to Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ney apna chehra dusri taraf pher kar aurton ko dekhna shuru kar diya. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wadi mohsir mein pahunchey to sawari ko qadrey tez kiya, phir us darmiyani raastey par chal padey jo badey jamre par pahunchata hai yahan tak key aap us jamre par ja pahunchey jo darkht key qarib hai. aap ney isey saat kankariyaan maarin, har kankari key sath Allahu-Akbar kehtey they. wo kankariyaan itni chhoti thin ke angoothey aur ungli sey pakad kar phenki ja saken. aap ney wadi key nasheb (dhalaan) mein khadey ho kar kankariyaan maarin. phir aap qurban gaah tashrif ley gaey aur apney haath sey tiresath (63) oonton ko nahar farmaya (qurban kiya). phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko (neza) diya to baqi oont unhoney nahar kiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen apney qurbani key janweron mein shareek kar liya tha. phir aap key hukm sey har oont ki eik boti ley kar handiyaa mein dali gaee aur pakaai gaee. dono ney ye gosht khaya aur uska shorbaa piya. phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tawaafe-ifaaza key liye Kaabe ki taraf tashrif ley gaey. aap ney Zohar ki namaz Makka Mukarrama mein ada ki. Abdul-Muttalib ki aulad key afrad Zamzam par pani pila rahey they, chunanche aap unkey paas tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : Abdul-Muttalib key beto ! (kuwein sey) pani nikalo, agar ye khof na hota ke log pani pilaney key mamley main tum par ghalib aa jaeyngey to main bhi tumharey sath pani nikalta. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik dol diya. aap ney us sey pani piya."
3075,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj key liye teen qism key Haj ki niyat sey rawana huye. kisi ney Haj aur Umerey dono key liye ehraam baandha tha, kisi ney sirf Haj ki niyat sey ehraam baandha tha, kisi ney sirf Umerey ki niyat sey labbaik kaha tha. to jisney Haj aur Umerey dono ki niyat sey ehraam baandha tha, is par Haj key aamaal ada karney tak koi (ehraam ki wajeh sey) haram honey wali chiz halal na hui. jisney sirf Haj ka ehraam baandha tha, is par bhi Haj key aamaal ada kar chukney tak koi haram honey wali chiz halal na hui. aur jisney sirf Umerey ki niyat ki thi, usney Kaba ka tawaf kiya, Safa aur Marwa ki saee ki, aur is par (ehraam ki wajeh sey) haram honey wali sab cheezen (ehraam kholney ki wajeh sey) halal ho gaeen yahan tak key wo Haj key liye ehraam baandhey."
3076,"Hazrat Sufiyan Sory (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney teen Haj ada farmaai. do Haj hijrat sey pehley aur eik Haj hijrat key baad Madina sey aa kar ada kiya. aur (is) Haj key sath umra bhi mila kar (Hajje-Qiran) ada kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qurbani key liye jo (oont) laye they, aur jo (oont) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ley kar aaye they wo sab mila kar sau oont they. un mein sey eik oont Abu-Jahal ka tha (jo musalmanon ko maale ghanimat mein hasil huwa tha), uski naak mein chaandi ka halqa tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath sey tiresath oont nahar (qurbaan) kiye jabkey baqi Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney nahar kiye. Sufiyan Sory (Rahimahullah) sey kaha gaya : unhen ye riwayat kis ney bayan ki hai? to unhoney kaha : Jaafar ney apney baap sey, unhoney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey. aur (doosri sanad) ibne-Abi Leila ney Hakm sey, unhoney Muqsim sey aur unhoney ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey."
3077,"Hazrat Hujjaaj bin Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jis shakhs ki haddi toot jaey ya langdaa ho jaey, wo ehraam khol dey. aur is par eik aur Haj karna lazim hai. (Hazrat ikrima (Rahimahullah) ney kaha :) mainey ye hadees Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhum sey bayan ki to unhoney kaha is (Hujjaaj bin Amr) ney sach kaha."
3078,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Abdullah bin Raafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Hujjaaj bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey ehraam waley ko rukawat pesh aaney key barey mein daryaft kiya to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki haddi toot jaey, ya bimar ho jaey, ya langdaa ho jaey, wo ehraam khol dey, aur is par agley saal Haj karna lazim hai. Hazrat Ikrima (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : mainey ye hadees Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhum sey bayan ki to unhoney kaha is (Hujjaaj bin Amr) ney sach kaha. Imam Abdur-Razzaaq ney kaha : mainey is riwayat ko Hisham sahab dustwaai ki kitab mein paya, chunanche usey main Maamar key paas laya to unhoney merey samney uski qirat ki ya mainey uskey samney uski qirat ki."
3079,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Maaqil (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main masjid mein Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja betha aur un sey is aayat key barey mein sawal kiya : (فَفِدْيَةٌ مِّن صِيَامٍ أَوْ صَدَقَةٍ أَوْ نُسُكٍ), 'to fidya hai rozon sey ya sadqey sey ya qurbani sey.'' Hazrat Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ye aayat merey hi barey mein nazil hui hai. mujhey sar mein (juon ki wajeh sey) takleef thi. mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kiya gaya jabkey juein (sar key baalon sey) jhad jhad kar merey chehrey par gir rahi thin to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mera ye khayal nahin tha ke tumhen is had tak takleef hogi jitni main (ab) dekh raha hun. kya tumhen eik bakri mil sakti hai? mainey kaha : ji nahin. tab ye aayat nazil hui : (فَفِدْيَةٌ مِّن صِيَامٍ أَوْ صَدَقَةٍ أَوْ نُسُكٍ), 'to fidya hai rozon sey ya sadqey sey ya qurbani sey.'' Sahaba ney farmaya : rozey to teen din key hain aur sadqa chhe miskinon ko diya jaey, har miskeen ko aadha saa ghalla diya jaey aur qurbani (ki miqdaar) eik bakri hai."
3080,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey jab juon sey takleef pahunchi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey hukm diya ke main sar mundaa dun aur teen din rozey rakhun ya chhe miskinon ko khana khila dun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko malum tha ke merey paas qurbani deney ki gunjaaish nahin."
3081,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney rozey aur ehraam ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai.
3082,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ehraam ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai kyonkey aap ko dard ho gaya tha.
3083,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ehraam ki haalat mein apney sar mein aisa tel dal letey they jis mein khushbu na hoti.
3084,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi key sawari key janwer ney uski gardan tod di jabkey wo shakhs ehraam ki haalat mein tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl do. aur usey uskey (ehraam key) do kapdon mein kafnaa do. uska sar aur chehra na dhaapna kyonkey wo qiyamat key din labbaik pukarta utheyga. eik dusri riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : uski sawari ney uski gardan mod di. is riwayat mein hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey khushbu key qarib na ley jana (khushbu na lagana), wo qiyamat key din labbaik pukarta huwa uthaya jaeyga."
3085,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : agar ehraam wala aadmi lagad bhagaa (bhediye jaisa eik khunkhaar janwer) maar dey to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is par eik mendhey ki qurbani dena lazim kiya hai aur us janwer ko shikar qarar diya hai."
3086,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke agar ehraam wala shatur murgh ka andaa tod dey to uskey barey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : uski qeemat ada kerey.
3087,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer fasiq hain, unhen Haram sey bahar aur Haram key andar (har jagah) qatl kiya ja sakta hai : sanp , chitkabra kawwa, choohaa, kaatney wala kutta aur cheel."
3088,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch janwer hain jinkey qatl karney waley par (ya farmaya : jinkey qatl karney mein) koi gunah nahin aur wo haram hain : bichchhu, kawwa , cheel , choohaa aur kaatney wala kutta."
3089,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ehraam wala shakhs in janweron ko qatl kar sakta hai : sanp , bichchhu, hamla karney wala darinda, kaatney wala kutta aur fasiq chuhiyaa. kisi ney Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : isey fasiq kyon kaha gaya hai? unhoney farmaya : isliye ke (eik raat) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aankh khuli to usney (chiragh ki jalti hui) batti pakad rakhi thi (aur mumkin tha) ke ghar ko aag laga dey."
3090,"Hazrat Saa'ab bin jasaama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Abvaa ya Vadaan key maqam par tha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas sey guzrey. mainey aap ki khidmat mein gorkhar (jangli gadhe) (ka gosht) tohfey key tor par pesh kiya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo mujhey wapis dey diya (qubul na kiya). jab aap ney merey chehrey par afsos key aasaar dekhey to farmaya : hum aap ko (ye tohfa) wapis to na kartey lekin hum ehraam ki haalat mein hain."
3091,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein shikar ka gosht pesh kiya gaya jabke aap ehraam mein they to aap ney wo na khaya."
3092,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen gorkhar (ka gosht) diya, aur hukm diya ke usey sathiyon mein taqseem kar den jabke wo sab ehraam baandhey huye they."
3093,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hudebiya (key waaqiye) key dino mein, main bhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath rawana huwa. aap key sathiyon ney ehraam baandha jabkey mainey ehraam na baandha. mujhey eik (jangli) gadhaa nazar aaya to mainey is par hamla kar key usey shikar kar liya, phir mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey uski kaifiyat arz ki aur ye bhi zikr kiya ke main ehraam mein nahin tha aur mainey aap (ko tohfa deney) key liye isey shikar kiya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sathiyon ko hukm diya ke isey kha lein, aur khud is mein sey (kuchh) na khaya kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya tha ke mainey isey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye shikar kiya hai."
3094,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina sey qurbaani ke jaanwer bhejtey they. main aap ki hudi key janweron key qalaadey bat kar tayyar karti thi, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi aisey kaam sey perhez nahin kartey they jis sey ehraam wala perhez karta hai."
3095,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hudi (qurbani key janweron) key liye qalaadey bat'ti thi to aap apni hudi ko qalaadey pehnatey they. phir un (janweron) ko (Makka Shareef) bhej detey. phir aap (Madina Shareef mein) qiyam pazeer rehtey aur kisi aisi chiz sey perhez na kartey jis sey ehraam wala perhez kiya karta hai."
3096,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik baar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh bakriyan hudi key tor par Baitullah bhejin to unhen qalaadey pahnaaey."
3097,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hudi key janwer ki kohaan par daain taraf ashaar kiya aur uska khoon poonchh diya. (hadees ke raawi) Ali bin Muhammad apni hadees mein bayan kartey hain : Zul-Hulefa mein (ashaar kiya) aur (janwer key) galey mein do jootiyaan dalin.
3098,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (hudi key janweron ko) qalaada pehnaya, ashaar kiya, aur unhen (Makka) bhej diya. aap ney un chizon sey perhez nahin kiya jin sey ehraam baandhney wala perhez kiya karta hai."
3099,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey hukm diya ke aap key oonton (ko zibeh wagheira kerney) ka bando-bast karun, aur un ki jhoolein aur khaalen taqseem kar dun, aur qassaab ko un mein sey kuchh na dun. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is (qassaab) ko hum (apney paas sey) detey hain."
3100,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney oonton mein hudi key tor par Abu-Jahal ka oont bhi shamil kiya, us (ki nakel) ka halqa chaandi ka tha."
3101,Hazrat Ayas bin Salma (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid (Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hudi key janweron main eik oont bhi tha.
3102,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hadi qudaid key maqam sey khareedi.
3103,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko dekha jo hudi key janwer (oont ya oontni) haankey liye ja raha tha. aap ney farmaya : is par sawar ho jao. usney kaha : ye to hudi ka janwer hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is par sawar ho ja. tera bhala ho.
3104,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik aadmi hudi ka janwer ley kar guzraa. aap ney farmaya : is par sawar ho ja. usney kaha : ye hudi ka janwer hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is par sawar ho ja. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath is par sawar (ho kar safar kartey) dekha jabke us (janwer) key galey mein (hudi key nishan key tor par) jooti bhi mojud thi.
3105,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Zuweb Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey sath qurbani key janwer (Haram mein) bheja kartey they. aur farma diya kartey they : jab un mein sey koi janwer thak jaey aur tujhey uskey marney ka khatra mehsus ho to usey nakhar kar dey, phir uski jooti uskey khoon mein dubo kar uskey pehlu par maar. to khud bhi us (key gosht) mein sey kuch na khana aur terey sathiyon mein sey bhi koi na khaye."
3106,"Hazrat Naajiya (bin Kaab bin Jundub) Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu), jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key oonton key nigraan they, un sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hudi ka jo janwer thak jaey uska kya karun? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey zibeh kar do aur uski jooti uskey khoon mein dubo kar uskey pehlu par maaro. phir usey logon key liye chhod do, wo usey kha lein."
3107,"Hazrat Alqama bin Nazlaa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut huye, phir Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) bhi faut ho gaey aur (un sab key zamaney mein ye kaifiyat thi ke) Makka key makanaat waqf kahlaatey they. jis ko zarurat hoti, un mein theherta aur jis ko zarurat na hoti kisi aur ko (un mein) thehraa deta."
3108,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Adi bin Humraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke apni oontni par hazuraa key maqam par khadey they aur farma rahey they. qism hai Allah ki ! to Allah ki zamin mein sab sey behtareen (aur afzal maqam) hai. aur Allah ki (saari) zamin mein sey to mujhey sab sey ziyada mehbub hai. qism hai Allah ki ! agar mujhey terey andar sey nikala na jata to main (kabhi) na nikalta."
3109,"Hazrat Safiya binte Shaiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Fateh Makka key saal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khutba irshad farmatey suna , aap ney farmaya : aey logo ! Allah ney Makka ko isi din Haram (mohtaram maqam) qarar dey diya tha jis din aasmano aur zamin ko paida kiya tha. wo qiyamat key din tak qabile ehtiraam rahega, (isliye) iska darkht na kaataa jaey, na is mein shikar ko bhagaayaa jaey, aur wahan giri padi chiz sirf wohi utha sakta hai jo aelan karna chahta ho.  Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : siwaye izkhir key. wo makaanon aur qabron mein istimal kiya jata hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : siwaye izkhir key."
3110,"Hazrat Ayash bin Abi Rabeea Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye ummat us waqt tak khair par rahegi jab tak (Harmain ki) is hurmat ki azmat ka khayal rakheygi jaisa ki haq tha. jab wo is fareezey (Harmain ki tazeem) ko zaya kerengey to tabah ho jaeyngey."
3111,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya. eman Madiney ki taraf isi tarah simat aayega jis tarah sanp simat kar apney bal ki taraf aa jata hai."
3112,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jo shakhs ye kar sakey ke Madina mein marey to zarur ye kerey. jo shakhs yahan faut hoga, main uskey haq mein gawahi dunga."
3113,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) tera khaleel aur tera Nabi tha. aur tu ney Ibrahim ki zaban par Makka ko Haram qarar diya. aey Allah ! main bhi tera banda aur tera Nabi hun. aur main is (Madiney) key (dono taraf key) siyah pattharon waley qataat ki darmiyani zamin ko Haram qarar deta hun. Abu-Marwaan (hadees key Raavi) ney kaha : siyah patharon waley dono qataat sey murad Madiney key mazkura dono qataat hain."
3114,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Madiney walon key sath burai ka irada kerega, Allah Taala usey is tarah ghula dega jis tarah pani mein namak ghul jata hai."
3115,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uhad aisa pahad hai jisey hum sey mohabbat hai aur hamein is sey mohabbat hai, aur wo jannat key eik tiley par hai. aur eir (pahad) jahannam key eik tiley par hai."
3116,"Hazrat Shaqeeq (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : eik shakhs ney Baitullah ko hadiya karney key liye merey haath kuchh dirham bhejey. main Kaba mein dakhil huwa to dekha ke Hazrat Sheeba (Raziallahu anhu) kursi par bethey huye they. mainey unhen wo (dirham) dey diye. unhoney kaha : kya ye tumharey hain? mainey kaha : nahin, agar merey hotey to main aap key paas na lata. unhoney kaha : tum ney ye baat kahi hai (to mujhey bhi eik baat yad aa gaee). Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) (eik din) usi jagah bethey they jahan tum (ab) bethey ho, unhoney farmaya : main (Kaabey sey) bahar nahin jaunga jab tak Kaabey ka maal nikal kar gharib musalmanon mein taqseem na kar dun. mainey kaha : aap ye kaam nahin kar saktey. unhoney farmaya : main ye kaam zarur karunga. lekin tum ney ye baat kyon kahi hai? mainey kaha : isliye ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye maal yahan dekha tha aur in ko is maal ki aap sey ziyada zarurat thi, un dono ney to isey hilaya bhi nahin. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) isi tarah khadey ho gaey aur (Kaabey sey) bahar tashrif ley gaey."
3117,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko Makka Mukarrama mein Ramzan ka mahina aa gaya aur usney hasabe istataat uskey rozey rakhey aur qiyam kiya, Allah Taala uskey liye kisi dusri jagah guzaarey huye eik lakh Ramzan key mahinon ka sawab likh dega. aur uskey liye har din key badley main eik ghulam azad karney ka sawab aur har raat key badley eik ghulam azad karney ka sawab likheyga, aur har din key badley mein Allah ki raah main eik sawari ka ghoda deney ka sawab likheyga. aur har din ki eik neki aur har raat ki eik neki likheyga."
3118,"Dawud bin Ajlan sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hamney Abu Uqaal key sath barish mein tawaf kiya. jab hamney tawaf mukammal kar liya to hum Maqame-Ibrahim key peechhey aagaey. Abu Uqaal ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key sath barish mein tawaf kiya. jab hamney tawaf mukammal kar liya to Maqame-Ibrahim par do rakatein padhin. tab Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney hum sey kaha : ab naey sirey sey apney amal ka hisab samjho. tumhari bakhshish ho gaee (pehley gunah sab maaf ho gaey). hamein bhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yehi irshad farmaya tha jab hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath barish mein tawaf kiya tha."
3119,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney Madina sey Makka tak pedal chal kar Haj kiya. aap ney farmaya : apni kamron par tehband achchhi tarah baandh lo (kamren kas lo). aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisi raftaar sey chaley jis mein kuchh daudnaa bhi shamil tha (itni tezi sey chaley ke daudney key qarib ho gaey)."
